ork City, 2008<ref>{{cite journal |last1=Abeles |first1=Sigmund |title=Prints, Drawings, Pastels, Paintings, and Sculpture |journal=The Old Print Shop Portfolio |date=May 2008 |volume=LXVII |issue=7 }}</ref>
